1c:["$","section",null,{"id":"about-jugarr","className":"seo-content-section","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"seo-content-block","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"seo-content-title font-display","children":"What is Jugarr? India's Campus Marketplace for Students"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"editorial-line","style":{"marginBottom":"24px"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"seo-content-body font-body","children":[["$","p",null,{"children":"Jugarr is India's first student-to-student campus marketplace — a platform where college students can buy, sell, trade, and earn within their own university ecosystem. Whether you need to sell old textbooks after exams, find affordable second-hand furniture for your hostel room, or buy a used bicycle for your daily campus commute, Jugarr makes it effortless."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The idea behind Jugarr is simple: every Indian college campus is already a thriving micro-economy. Students sell handwritten notes, trade gadgets, offer tutoring, design projects, and run small services — but they do it through scattered WhatsApp groups, notice boards, and word of mouth. Jugarr brings all of this into one trusted, organized student marketplace."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"On Jugarr, you can list second-hand books, study notes, electronics, furniture, and cycles for sale. You can also offer skills-based services like graphic design, video editing, coding, content writing, and academic tutoring — and get paid directly by peers on your campus. Students looking for internships, freelance gigs, or project collaborators can discover opportunities posted by fellow students and campus organizations."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"What makes Jugarr different from generic classifieds or e-commerce apps is its campus-first approach. Every user is a verified college student. Every transaction happens within your college community — face to face, in your hostel lobby, library, or canteen. There are no platform commissions, no shipping hassles, and no strangers. Just students helping students."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Jugarr is currently rolling out across colleges in India. Join the waitlist today to bring the student marketplace to your campus and become a founding member of your college's Jugarr community."}]]}]]}]}]}]
